(58, 'ASUS All-in-One PC A6421UKH-BC024R', 'NwK1P6w62X', '<h2 style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit; padding-right: 0.5em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1em; font-weight: bold; font-family: DINPro, arial; position: relative; bottom: -1px; color: #009dd3; float: none; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">Un tout-en-un professionnel compact, performant et pratique</h2>\r\n<p><br style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit; color: #141414; font-family: arial, verdana, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;" /><span style="color: #141414; font-family: arial, verdana, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">Con&ccedil;u pour les professionnels, l\'ordinateur tout-en-un&nbsp;</span><strong style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit; color: #141414; font-family: arial, verdana, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">ASUS&nbsp;A6421</strong><span style="color: #141414; font-family: arial, verdana, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;vous offre les performances, la fiabilit&eacute; et la simplicit&eacute; d\'utilisation dont vous avez besoin pour travailler efficacement au quotidien. Son &eacute;cran de 21.5 pouces Full HD (1920 x 1080) offre &eacute;galement un excellent confort visuel.</span></p>\r\n<div style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit; color: #141414; font-family: arial, verdana, geneva, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;"><br style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit;" />L\'ASUS All-in-One PC A6421UKH-BC024R offre d\'excellentes performances gr&acirc;ce &agrave; son puissant processeur<strong style="border-style: none; border-color: inherit;">&nbsp;Intel Core i5-6400</strong>, ses 8 Go de m&